---
title: Sweet-Soy Chicken & Garlic Rice with Garlic Greens & Crispy Shallots
description: We’ve finally spotted the ultimate chicken dish on the horizon. These chicken steaks will make your mouth water and calm stormy
seas when seasoned in sweet and soy flavours. It’s all steam ahead when you get a taste of the ginger veggies with a hint of
honey and soy. Drop the anchor, it’s time to eat!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65030dbdddf45550bcf9f3c8-96f80240.jpeg
